1
00:01:24,110 --> 00:01:29,910
[Sunshine of My Life]

2
00:01:30,610 --> 00:01:32,880
[Episode 13]

3
00:01:48,400 --> 00:01:49,990
Come in.

4
00:01:51,560 --> 00:01:53,890
- Mingxuan.
- Uncle Xia.

5
00:01:54,550 --> 00:02:00,020
Not bad, Mingxuan. Really not bad.

6
00:02:00,020 --> 00:02:04,040
Today, I received Daily Fashion's report.

7
00:02:04,040 --> 00:02:06,560
Sales keep rising.

8
00:02:07,780 --> 00:02:08,680
The younger generation will indeed surpass the older one.

9
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:11,850
We just launched it so we won't know about the specifics of the sales

10
00:02:11,850 --> 00:02:14,620
until later on.

11
00:02:15,200 --> 00:02:16,920
Okay, thank you.

12
00:02:16,920 --> 00:02:21,260
The current results are already impressive. Don't give yourself too high of expectations.

13
00:02:21,260 --> 00:02:25,060
It'll cause my daughter to throw herself into work every single day.

14
00:02:25,060 --> 00:02:26,760
Look at you.

15
00:02:27,820 --> 00:02:31,530
Xueling has been working hard lately.

16
00:02:31,530 --> 00:02:34,430
I've talked about this seriously with her, too.

17
00:02:34,430 --> 00:02:38,900
I told her that her job right now is design director,

18
00:02:38,900 --> 00:02:41,680
so she should do her own work well.

19
00:02:41,680 --> 00:02:44,660
As for the rest, there's you.

20
00:02:44,660 --> 00:02:46,720
Guess what she told me.

21
00:02:46,720 --> 00:02:50,590
She said it was because you need to do all the rest of the work,

22
00:02:50,590 --> 00:02:54,360
so she has to share the burden with you.

23
00:02:55,490 --> 00:02:59,090
Xueling really has helped me a lot.

24
00:02:59,970 --> 00:03:03,540
I did not come here today with the intention to blame you.

25
00:03:03,540 --> 00:03:07,620
But I am going to criticize you on behalf of my wife.

26
00:03:07,630 --> 00:03:10,480
Your Aunt Xia is not happy and nags me every day,

27
00:03:10,480 --> 00:03:13,630
saying that we raised our daughter for nothing.

28
00:03:13,630 --> 00:03:16,510
We have raised her for your Tang family instead.

29
00:03:16,510 --> 00:03:19,270
Look! If she is not at your house,

30
00:03:19,270 --> 00:03:24,040
then she is at work. Your aunt doesn't even see her daughter twice a week.

31
00:03:24,040 --> 00:03:26,990
You also know, when women get old,

32
00:03:26,990 --> 00:03:30,790
they like to nag, but I have relayed your Aunt Xia's words.

33
00:03:31,460 --> 00:03:34,610
Uncle Xia, have some tea.

34
00:03:34,610 --> 00:03:37,400
I was indeed inconsiderate in this matter.

35
00:03:37,400 --> 00:03:39,060
I assure you...

36
00:03:39,060 --> 00:03:43,390
I will try my best to not have Xueling work overtime so she can go home earlier to spend time with you and Aunt.

37
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:46,400
That's not what I mean. She acts on her accord.

38
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:49,240
If she is happy, what can we do?

39
00:03:49,240 --> 00:03:52,400
As long as your family treats Xueling well in the future, it is fine.

40
00:03:52,400 --> 00:03:54,740
Don't make us go to your house in the end

41
00:03:54,740 --> 00:03:56,510
and take what we deserve with interest.

42
00:03:56,510 --> 00:03:59,150
That would be embarrassing.

43
00:04:00,900 --> 00:04:05,480
Don't worry, our family will not let her down.

44
00:04:05,480 --> 00:04:06,920
Okay.

45
00:04:06,920 --> 00:04:10,970
Mingxuan, I will remember these words of yours.

46
00:04:10,970 --> 00:04:16,730
Right! What did I want to discuss with you today?

47
00:04:16,730 --> 00:04:19,080
We were talking about trivial matters for so long.

48
00:04:19,080 --> 00:04:23,960
Oh, right! The designer that caused trouble backstage at the competition last time...

49
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:25,680
Mingxuan,

50
00:04:26,840 --> 00:04:31,620
why are her clothes still on the platform? What are you thinking?

51
00:04:33,570 --> 00:04:36,770
Uncle Xia, perhaps you are not familiar with the whole incident.

52
00:04:36,770 --> 00:04:38,840
The situation has already been cleared up.

53
00:04:38,840 --> 00:04:40,970
You don't have to worry.

54
00:04:40,970 --> 00:04:44,260
Mingxuan, this is not about clearing matters up.

55
00:04:44,260 --> 00:04:49,160
Look! Although you work very hard and you have achieved great results,

56
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:51,570
I have to criticize you in this matter.

57
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:55,550
You have made a common mistake that all the young make. Do you know what it is called?

58
00:04:55,550 --> 00:04:59,510
It's called short-sightedness, only focusing on the immediate benefits.

59
00:04:59,510 --> 00:05:01,180
Right now she is really popular

60
00:05:01,180 --> 00:05:05,640
and has some fame. But you know what? Her popularity comes from notoriety.

61
00:05:05,640 --> 00:05:08,110
Using her to attract attention,

62
00:05:08,110 --> 00:05:11,310
have you thought of Mingyuan's image?

63
00:05:13,270 --> 00:05:15,850
I have also heard

64
00:05:15,850 --> 00:05:18,370
that Xueling does not agree on this matter as well.

65
00:05:18,370 --> 00:05:23,050
Look! You are the president of the company.

66
00:05:23,050 --> 00:05:25,130
She is the design director.

67
00:05:25,130 --> 00:05:29,180
I think you two need to discuss the specific affairs of the company

68
00:05:29,180 --> 00:05:32,650
just like how your father and I were back then. Right?

69
00:05:32,650 --> 00:05:36,020
Even if it’s something he had already decided,

70
00:05:36,020 --> 00:05:38,030
as long as I disagree,

71
00:05:38,030 --> 00:05:40,970
- he couldn't go through with it...
- Uncle Xia.

72
00:05:40,970 --> 00:05:44,880
I run and manage this company now.

73
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:47,010
Right, right. You are extremely right.

74
00:05:47,010 --> 00:05:51,310
This company is now yours to manage.

75
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:55,040
We shouldn't get too involved and shouldn't bother you anymore.

76
00:05:57,300 --> 00:06:01,330
Very good. This work you are doing now...

77
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:04,750
I'm very satisfied with the sales performance.

78
00:06:04,750 --> 00:06:08,210
I believe your father is also very satisfied.

79
00:06:08,210 --> 00:06:10,020
Look, I'm old now.

80
00:06:10,020 --> 00:06:13,460
Like your Aunt Xia, I have started to nag.

81
00:06:13,460 --> 00:06:15,850
I won't bother you anymore.

82
00:06:17,620 --> 00:06:20,940
You just discuss with Xueling the designer's matter.

83
00:06:20,940 --> 00:06:23,830
- Uncle Xia, take care.
- All right.

84
00:06:32,090 --> 00:06:36,230
I am very sorry, we're not hiring right now.

85
00:06:36,230 --> 00:06:40,260
Sorry, we are currently not hiring.

86
00:06:45,070 --> 00:06:46,740
[Potential Jobs List - waitressing at a western restaurant]

87
00:06:59,310 --> 00:07:03,650
[Chez M. Huang]

88
00:07:13,570 --> 00:07:17,200
Hello, Cheng Yang. I want to ask if you have time right now.

89
00:07:18,340 --> 00:07:21,240
I'm really sorry to call you over in such a hurry.

90
00:07:21,250 --> 00:07:23,430
- It's all right.
- Be careful.

91
00:07:23,430 --> 00:07:26,090
The boss must have asked this of you because of safety reasons.

92
00:07:26,090 --> 00:07:28,410
- You're here.
- Boss, this is my guarantor.

93
00:07:28,410 --> 00:07:29,530
Hello.

94
00:07:29,530 --> 00:07:31,410
Wait a moment.

95
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,030
Have a seat over there first.

96
00:07:35,030 --> 00:07:36,690
- Okay.
- Okay.

97
00:07:51,670 --> 00:07:52,900
Have a glass of water first.

98
00:07:52,900 --> 00:07:55,010
- Thank you, Boss.
- Thank you.

99
00:07:56,800 --> 00:07:59,520
Please show me your residence permit.

100
00:08:02,610 --> 00:08:04,050
Here.

101
00:08:06,770 --> 00:08:08,940
I have been here for four years now.

102
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:21,280
You two don't look like bad people, either.

103
00:08:21,280 --> 00:08:22,990
Of course, we are not bad people.

104
00:08:22,990 --> 00:08:27,700
Usually, we start at 10:00 a.m. every morning to prepare the materials for lunch.

105
00:08:27,700 --> 00:08:29,450
We open at 11:00 a.m.

106
00:08:29,450 --> 00:08:31,300
Around 1:00 p.m, we are busiest.

107
00:08:31,300 --> 00:08:33,870
For the afternoon service, we are open until 2:30 p.m.

108
00:08:33,870 --> 00:08:38,480
In the evening, we open at 7:00 p.m. and close at 10:00 p.m.

109
00:08:38,480 --> 00:08:41,260
Boss, it is like this, because I am still in school,

110
00:08:41,260 --> 00:08:44,820
can I work in accordance with my class schedule?

111
00:08:44,820 --> 00:08:48,700
No problem. You can be in charge of closing.

112
00:08:48,700 --> 00:08:50,800
What does closing mean?

113
00:08:50,800 --> 00:08:56,590
It means that after closing every day, you are in charge of washing the dishes and kitchen.

114
00:08:56,590 --> 00:09:00,570
The hygiene requirements in France are stricter, so we have to clean every day.

115
00:09:00,570 --> 00:09:02,690
That's right. You seem experienced.

116
00:09:02,690 --> 00:09:06,800
When I first came, I also worked in a kitchen for two and a half years.

117
00:09:06,800 --> 00:09:09,570
If possible, I hope that during the weekends,

118
00:09:09,570 --> 00:09:12,280
you can work both the early and late shifts.

119
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,610
Okay, no problem.

120
00:09:13,610 --> 00:09:16,580
Since that is so, you can start tomorrow.

121
00:09:16,580 --> 00:09:18,080
Okay.

122
00:09:36,610 --> 00:09:40,400
If it can be done, it will really help Mingyuan a lot.

123
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:47,190
Okay.

124
00:09:47,190 --> 00:09:50,090
We'll discuss the details in person.

125
00:09:51,410 --> 00:09:53,810
Your French is not bad.

126
00:09:53,810 --> 00:09:56,540
It's a pity there's no place for you to use it here.

127
00:09:58,120 --> 00:10:01,510
Such a rare guest. Is there something you need?

128
00:10:01,510 --> 00:10:05,550
I'm here this time with good intentions.

129
00:10:05,550 --> 00:10:07,620
I came to say goodbye.

130
00:10:07,620 --> 00:10:12,140
Thinking about life without you in the future... seems boring.

131
00:10:13,680 --> 00:10:17,410
Let me show you something. You should be interested.

132
00:10:19,530 --> 00:10:21,020
[Itinerary: From Pudong, Shanghai to Paris, France.]

133
00:10:23,130 --> 00:10:27,040
Why would you think I would be interested in this?

134
00:10:27,040 --> 00:10:29,690
I'll be going to the airport in a bit.

135
00:10:29,690 --> 00:10:32,260
If you have anything to tell Mo Fei, tell me.

136
00:10:32,260 --> 00:10:34,310
I'll help you relay the message.

137
00:10:36,830 --> 00:10:41,110
There's no need for that. You're not the only person with a mouth.

138
00:10:42,870 --> 00:10:46,980
Then... have a safe journey.

139
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:54,710
It is upsetting to be abandoned, right?

140
00:11:01,920 --> 00:11:04,800
You are becoming more and more interesting.

141
00:11:10,590 --> 00:11:13,730
You've caused my sister to experience feelings of sadness.

142
00:11:14,480 --> 00:11:17,060
I will also let you experience it.

143
00:11:17,060 --> 00:11:18,760
I'm leaving.

144
00:11:21,560 --> 00:11:23,650
Close the door for me.

145
00:11:24,660 --> 00:11:26,530
So sensible.

146
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:49,410
♫ You'll surely be sad ♫

147
00:11:50,770 --> 00:11:55,980
♫ You'll surely miss me ♫

148
00:11:56,980 --> 00:12:00,400
♫ Yet you're free and easygoing as always ♫

149
00:12:00,400 --> 00:12:04,720
♫ You emotionlessly face me ♫

150
00:12:04,720 --> 00:12:07,630
I hope you will always keep him by your side.

151
00:12:09,300 --> 00:12:11,500
Whenever you see him,

152
00:12:12,580 --> 00:12:14,500
you will think of me.

153
00:12:18,920 --> 00:12:25,050
♫ You may miss me very much ♫

154
00:12:25,050 --> 00:12:28,640
♫ Congratulations, you've wrapped up the performance early ♫

155
00:12:28,640 --> 00:12:31,650
♫ A sequel for my tragic role ♫

156
00:12:31,650 --> 00:12:34,760
♫ in a one-man show ♫

157
00:12:34,760 --> 00:12:37,860
♫ was given all to me ♫

158
00:12:38,840 --> 00:12:40,440
Hi.

159
00:12:41,020 --> 00:12:45,530
I am now in Paris.

160
00:12:47,190 --> 00:12:52,110
For now, I'm staying in a friend's living room.

161
00:12:52,110 --> 00:12:55,180
♫ Another universe lets me disappear ♫

162
00:12:55,180 --> 00:12:57,510
At the airport,

163
00:12:58,490 --> 00:13:02,210
what was the meaning of everything you said to me?

164
00:13:02,210 --> 00:13:06,490
♫ I'll no longer bother your life ♫

165
00:13:09,990 --> 00:13:14,480
What's the point of recording this? Even if I record this, I won't broadcast it.

166
00:13:15,220 --> 00:13:18,980
Even if he hears it, so what?

167
00:13:23,050 --> 00:13:27,240
Mo Fei, why aren't you sleeping yet?

168
00:13:27,240 --> 00:13:30,250
You artists are so strange.

169
00:13:30,250 --> 00:13:32,680
Sitting here looking at the moon in the middle of the night.

170
00:13:32,680 --> 00:13:35,450
Why aren't you sleeping either? Come and sit.

171
00:13:35,450 --> 00:13:38,600
I'm doing business right now.

172
00:13:38,600 --> 00:13:43,110
At this time right now, all those working women in China

173
00:13:43,110 --> 00:13:45,610
are exchanging their shopping experiences.

174
00:13:45,610 --> 00:13:48,630
How can I miss out on this time?

175
00:13:49,810 --> 00:13:53,550
Has that guy responded to your WeChat Moment?

176
00:13:57,180 --> 00:14:02,080
That can't be right. A normal man should have some reaction.

177
00:14:03,820 --> 00:14:07,620
That's why... I said

178
00:14:07,620 --> 00:14:09,650
he probably already has a girlfriend.

179
00:14:09,650 --> 00:14:12,160
He has a girlfriend yet he still chased you to the airport

180
00:14:12,160 --> 00:14:14,720
and gifted you that doll.

181
00:14:15,450 --> 00:14:17,800
That doesn't make sense.

182
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:20,770
It actually doesn't make sense if he doesn't have a girlfriend.

183
00:14:20,770 --> 00:14:24,380
You have no idea. That girl is really beautiful.

184
00:14:25,750 --> 00:14:27,340
Do you think you're bad-looking?

185
00:14:27,340 --> 00:14:30,290
You are not bad-looking, all right?

186
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:34,400
But they are childhood sweethearts,

187
00:14:34,400 --> 00:14:36,580
and their families are well matched.

188
00:14:36,580 --> 00:14:38,590
In the eyes of outsiders,

189
00:14:38,590 --> 00:14:42,230
they are a match made in Heaven.

190
00:14:42,230 --> 00:14:45,440
Then that's a bit difficult to deal with.

191
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:48,910
See, you think so too. Right?

192
00:14:49,770 --> 00:14:53,120
It's not important how the two of us think.

193
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:57,210
What's important is, do you like him?

194
00:15:00,650 --> 00:15:04,240
- I don't like him right now.
- See, then it's resolved, right?

195
00:15:04,240 --> 00:15:08,410
Since you've already thought it through so clearly, what is there that you cannot let go of?

196
00:15:08,410 --> 00:15:12,610
Let me tell you. Starting tomorrow,

197
00:15:13,900 --> 00:15:15,840
forget him.

198
00:15:15,840 --> 00:15:19,450
The "forest" in France is waiting for you.

199
00:15:19,450 --> 00:15:22,080
My dear Miss Mo Fei,

200
00:15:23,270 --> 00:15:26,470
do you remember the handsome guy downstairs? Do you like him?

201
00:15:28,440 --> 00:15:31,130
- Give back the little prince.
- No.

202
00:15:31,130 --> 00:15:33,660
- Hurry.
- No.

203
00:15:38,810 --> 00:15:41,940
- Brother Xuan.
- What's the hurry?

204
00:15:41,940 --> 00:15:44,330
The financing department of the embroidery workshop's construction site has been pressing for money.

205
00:15:44,330 --> 00:15:46,120
They say our funds never arrived.

206
00:15:46,120 --> 00:15:49,160
So I checked. I heard that Xia Zhendong's people

207
00:15:49,160 --> 00:15:52,240
have been blocking the funds from being distributed.

208
00:15:53,520 --> 00:15:55,200
Hello.

209
00:15:55,200 --> 00:15:57,500
I just found out.

210
00:15:57,500 --> 00:15:59,570
I'm heading over right now.

211
00:16:00,160 --> 00:16:01,840
Brother Xuan, where are we going right now?

212
00:16:01,840 --> 00:16:03,480
The Xia family's residence.

213
00:16:26,590 --> 00:16:29,240
- Auntie.
- Mingxuan.

214
00:16:29,240 --> 00:16:31,270
You haven't come over for quite a while.

215
00:16:31,270 --> 00:16:34,200
- Have you eaten breakfast?
- I've already eaten.

216
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:38,240
- Where is Uncle Xia?
- He's upstairs.

217
00:16:38,240 --> 00:16:42,390
I don't know why but he's been arguing with Xueling since this morning.

218
00:16:42,390 --> 00:16:43,980
Go inside and sit first. I'll get him for you.

219
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:45,400
Okay.

220
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:53,230
Why are you here, Mingxuan?

221
00:16:53,230 --> 00:16:56,150
Don't argue with your dad. It's not worth it.

222
00:16:56,150 --> 00:16:58,240
I'll talk to Uncle Xia in a bit.

223
00:16:58,240 --> 00:17:01,300
He was wrong in the first place.

224
00:17:01,300 --> 00:17:04,920
How am I wrong? How am I wrong?

225
00:17:04,920 --> 00:17:06,600
Mingxuan.

226
00:17:08,850 --> 00:17:13,480
Look, about the construction funds, I really didn't want to make it difficult for you.

227
00:17:13,480 --> 00:17:16,710
But I also have my own difficulties right now.

228
00:17:16,710 --> 00:17:22,820
Uncle Xia, didn't we already confirm the budget at the stockholders' meeting?

229
00:17:22,820 --> 00:17:24,770
What's happened now?

230
00:17:24,770 --> 00:17:27,190
There are indeed some sudden developments.

231
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:29,910
You know it, too. Our Mingyuan is a big enterprise.

232
00:17:29,910 --> 00:17:32,800
There are places other than yours where we need to spend money.

233
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:36,440
How about this, Mingxuan? We each take a step back.

234
00:17:36,440 --> 00:17:40,400
It's not that we won't do the embroidery workshop, but just postpone it for a little while.

235
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:45,330
Dad, a lot of people have been watching the failed SLC acquisition.

236
00:17:45,330 --> 00:17:47,690
We really can't have anything go wrong with the embroidery workshop.

237
00:17:47,690 --> 00:17:50,030
We're just waiting for money in order to start the construction right now.

238
00:17:50,030 --> 00:17:53,500
If the follow-up funding doesn't come through, then the money spent in the earlier stage will be wasted.

239
00:17:53,500 --> 00:17:55,810
I know that many elders aren't accepting of it.

240
00:17:55,810 --> 00:17:57,750
But you are different from them.

241
00:17:57,750 --> 00:17:59,730
You must be able to see the big picture.

242
00:17:59,730 --> 00:18:02,160
How do I not look at the big picture?

243
00:18:02,160 --> 00:18:04,160
I am currently considering the overall big picture.

244
00:18:04,160 --> 00:18:07,260
It's for Mingxuan's sake. What do you know?

245
00:18:07,260 --> 00:18:10,570
Mingxuan, in these past few years where you're in charge,

246
00:18:10,570 --> 00:18:14,140
everyone saw the outstanding results and robust endeavors.

247
00:18:14,140 --> 00:18:16,210
You have lead Mingyuan to move forward.

248
00:18:16,210 --> 00:18:18,650
However, without meaning to,

249
00:18:18,650 --> 00:18:21,100
you've neglected some of the old guys.

250
00:18:21,100 --> 00:18:22,880
Their hearts got cold.

251
00:18:22,880 --> 00:18:27,660
When people lose their hearts and their hearts are cold, it doesn't matter how big the company is,

252
00:18:27,660 --> 00:18:30,490
it will collapse at the drop of a hat. Right?

