00:36:54,320 --> 00:36:57,530
Come be my assistant at Cayman's press conference.

514
00:36:57,530 --> 00:36:59,610
I'm not interested.

515
00:36:59,610 --> 00:37:03,080
Can you consider it for a while? Aren't you being too perfunctory?

516
00:37:03,080 --> 00:37:05,710
Okay, I'll consider it.

517
00:37:07,820 --> 00:37:09,880
I'm not interested.

518
00:37:10,430 --> 00:37:12,230
Mo Fei...

519
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:16,920
Do you know what it means to be my assistant?

520
00:37:16,920 --> 00:37:19,950
- If this press conference—
- Director Fang, I still have to work and time is ticking.

521
00:37:19,950 --> 00:37:22,150
I'll buy you coffee another day. I appreciate your kindness.

522
00:37:22,150 --> 00:37:25,340
Bye-bye, bye-bye! We'll set up another time to meet.

523
00:37:27,530 --> 00:37:30,100
You really don't know how well I treat you.

524
00:37:32,290 --> 00:37:34,680
- Dad.
- Yes.

525
00:37:34,680 --> 00:37:39,200
- Why haven't you gone to bed yet? Its so late.
- I just finished talking with your Uncle Wei on the phone.

526
00:37:40,280 --> 00:37:43,940
- Has the embroidery workshop's problem been solved?
- It's been solved.

527
00:37:43,940 --> 00:37:45,930
What are your thoughts?

528
00:37:46,570 --> 00:37:49,230
I'm a junior, so there are many things that I can't say.

529
00:37:49,230 --> 00:37:53,880
Uncle Xia must have his own thoughts.

530
00:37:54,980 --> 00:37:57,260
You know it in your heart.

531
00:38:04,450 --> 00:38:09,200
Oh, right! About SLC, I plan to make a trip there myself.

532
00:38:09,200 --> 00:38:11,800
So far we've been communicating over the distance.

533
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:13,690
I think this whole thing is not progressing much.

534
00:38:13,690 --> 00:38:17,010
If we talk in person, the result may be different.

535
00:38:17,010 --> 00:38:19,080
Going to France?

536
00:38:21,370 --> 00:38:26,920
That's good, too. To do business, we must have views about the ecosystem, the overall situation, and the future.

537
00:38:26,920 --> 00:38:29,080
We cannot only pay attention to our own industry.

538
00:38:29,080 --> 00:38:32,860
We must have our own core technology and have a view toward the future.

539
00:38:32,860 --> 00:38:35,880
If you can successfully acquire SLC this time,

540
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:39,040
it is a crucial step for Mingyuan.

541
00:38:39,840 --> 00:38:42,820
Don't worry, I'll take care of it well.

542
00:38:50,640 --> 00:38:52,470
Big...

543
00:38:57,210 --> 00:38:59,020
Big news!

544
00:38:59,020 --> 00:39:01,440
